Context: The Centre For Business at George Brown College holds regular Information Sessions to explore their Business programs, which can be attended in-person or online. Interested individuals can register for an In-Person Info Session or an Online Info Session. The college also has a land acknowledgment. To receive updates about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours and more, visitors are encouraged to Sign Up Now. Contact information includes the phone number 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559, and email address ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The college has a Social Media Hub for visitors to explore. Please note that the information contained in this website is subject to change without notice. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
